<section class="contentitem">
    <h2 id="viralplushtoys">Design Test for a Company that Makes Plush Toys</h2>
    <span>These are design samples for a company that sells plush toys using viral marketing strategies.<br>Ceres Miller, 2024</span>
    <hr>
    <p>These are 9 plush toy designs. The first 3 are about pairs, (keep one, give one) the next 3 are about reveals (something hidden inside, for example) and the last 3 are studies of viral content.</p>
    <blockquote><p>Fuzzy Stars create premium and playful plush toys aimed at adults. The more viral the toy the better. This is because we put a massive emphasis onto marketing across social media. We have noticed that reveal toys and toys that come in pairs (keep one, give one) do well.</p></blockquote>
    <p>The first slide outlines my approach.</p>
